nalysis_findings": "基于收集到的指标数据，我对系统在2025-06-06T19:10:06Z到2025-06-06T19:33:06Z期间的异常进行了分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-01\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存资源紧张，node_memory_usage_rate从40.46%上升到58.18%（增长35.93%），node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes从10.4GB减少到7.5GB（下降33.14%），导致运行在该节点上的服务性能下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate: 40.46% → 58.18% (+35.93%), node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes: 10.4GB → 7.5GB (-33.14%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU使用率异常飙升，pod_cpu_usage从0.01增加到0.6（增长193.44%），同时rrt从3420.58ms增加到13822.8ms（增长120.65%），rrt_max从42833ms增加到95522ms（增长76.16%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.01 → 0.6 (+193.44%), rrt: 3420.58ms → 13822.8ms (+120.65%), rrt_max: 42833ms → 95522ms (+76.16%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务错误率异常，error_ratio和client_error_ratio的p99值从0%上升到26%，同时rrt_max从3743.5ms增加到4544ms（增长19.32%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio p99: 0% → 26%, client_error_ratio p99: 0% → 26%, rrt_max: 3743.5ms → 4544ms (+19.32%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU使用率异常，pod_cpu_usage从0增加到0.6（增长200%），rrt_max从42960.5ms增加到87009ms（增长67.78%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0 → 0.6 (+200%), rrt_max: 42960.5ms → 87009ms (+67.78%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU使用率异常，pod_cpu_usage从0增加到0.6（增长200%），rrt从5814.86ms增加到8833.25ms（增长41.21%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0 → 0.6 (+200%), rrt: 5814.86ms → 8833.25ms (+41.21%)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结：**\n\n1. **主要问题**：aiops-k8s-01节点内存资源紧张，这可能是导致多个服务性能下降的根因\n2. **关键影响**：adservice的三个Pod实例都出现了CPU使用率飙升和响应时间显著增加\n3. **错误表现**：cartservice-0出现了较高的错误率（26% p99